<p><strong><a href="x50870.xml" style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">Campus History</a><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;"> </span></strong> <br /><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">Everything in this category has to do with Brigham Young University-Idaho. Including Devotionals, Yearbooks, and Past Presidents.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;"><strong><a href="x50829.xml" title="Manuscript Collections">Manuscripts&nbsp;Collections</a></strong><br />The manuscript collections of the Brigham Young University-Idaho Special Collections include Local History items and are donated in part by patrons to form the hand written version of a book, article, document, or other work prepared by the author. They contain material of outstanding research importance for all periods, countries and disciplines.&nbsp;<a href="x50751.xml">File Manuscripts</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="x50752.xml">Life Sketches</a>&nbsp;are both located here as well. We have also placed the&nbsp;<a href="x50835.xml">Oral History Interviews</a>&nbsp;in this category.<br />Use&nbsp;<a href="x47750.xml">finding aids</a>&nbsp;to help narrow your search. </span></p>
<p><strong><a class="intLink" href="x50839.xml" title="Special Collections">Special Collections</a> </strong><br />Special Collections consist of material that has been collected on a certain subject area. These materials are often printed material including books but can vary in the type of items entered into the collection depending on the collecting area.<br /><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">Most of these collections can be found by searching through the&nbsp;</span><a href="http://hip.byui.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?profile=#focus" style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;" title="Library Catalog" target="_blank">Library Catalog</a><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">.</span></p>
<p><img alt="Henry B. Eyring Devotional" src="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/utils/ajaxhelper/?CISOROOT=BYUICampus&amp;CISOPTR=1361&amp;action=2&amp;DMSCALE=75&amp;DMWIDTH=450&amp;DMHEIGHT=313&amp;DMX=0&amp;DMY=0&amp;DMTEXT=devotional&amp;DMROTATE=0" style="float: right;" title="Henry B. Erying Devotional" /></p>
<p><strong><a href="x48451.xml" style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">Newspapers/Publications&nbsp;</a> </strong><br /><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">The Newspapers found in the Brigham Young University-Idaho Special Collections contain the current Scroll and the first papers printed here at BYU-Idaho along with several local papers collected by Special Collections. Many of these papers can be found online by clicking the links.</span></p>
<p><strong><a href="x48450.xml">Photographs</a></strong><a href="x48449.xml"></a><a href="x48450.xml"><br /></a>The photograph collections of the Brigham Young University-Idaho Special Collections are collected by University photographers and also donated in part by patrons. We also have a <a href="x48456.xml">digital photo collection </a>which contains almost all of our photos, which can be found online.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true"><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="x50412" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly